---
const title = "美股分析 - 热门投资信号";
const description = "最新美股分析报告，深度分析 AAPL、TSLA、NVDA 等热门股票";
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="description" content={description} />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>{title}</title>
    <style>
        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
        body { font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; background: #f9fafb; color: #1f2937; }
        .container { max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
        .back-link { display: inline-block; color: #667eea; text-decoration: none; margin-bottom: 20px; }
        h1 { font-size: 2.5rem; color: #1e40af; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
        .banner { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fffbeb 0%, #fef3c7 100%); border-left: 4px solid #f59e0b; padding: 20px; margin: 30px 0; border-radius: 8px; }
        .banner h2 { color: #92400e; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 1.5rem; }
        .grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr)); gap: 1.5rem; margin-top: 2rem; }
        .card { border: 1px solid #ddd; border-radius: 12px; padding: 1.5rem; text-decoration: none; color: inherit; transition: all 0.3s; box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); background: white; }
        .card:hover { box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); transform: translateY(-2px); }
        .badge { display: inline-block; background: #e3f2fd; color: #1976d2; padding: 4px 12px; border-radius: 20px; font-size: 0.8em; margin-bottom: 10px; }
        .card h2 { color: #667eea; margin: 10px 0; font-size: 1.3rem; }
        .card p { color: #666; line-height: 1.6; font-size: 0.95rem; }
        footer { text-align: center; padding: 40px 0; color: #666; margin-top: 60px; border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <a href="/" class="back-link">← 返回首页</a>
        
        <h1>📈 美股分析</h1>
        
        <div class="banner">
            <h2>🚀 全新改版即将上线</h2>
            <p>我们正在为您准备更深入的美股分析报告，包含技术面、基本面、资金流向等多维度分析</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="grid">
            <a href="/stock-analysis/aapl-20260331/" class="card">
                <span class="badge">即将推出</span>
                <h2>🍎 Apple (AAPL) 深度分析</h2>
                <p>短期回调还是长期买入机会？关键支撑位 245 美元成焦点</p>
            </a>
            
            <a href="/stock-analysis/tsla-20260331/" class="card">
                <span class="badge">即将推出</span>
                <h2>🚗 Tesla (TSLA) 深度分析</h2>
                <p>短期回调还是长期买入机会？关键指标揭示后市走势</p>
            </a>
            
            <a href="/stock-analysis/nvda-20260331/" class="card">
                <span class="badge">即将推出</span>
                <h2>🎮 Nvidia (NVDA) 深度分析</h2>
                <p>关键支撑与 AI 增长逻辑全解读</p>
            </a>
            
            <a href="/stock-analysis/msft-20260331/" class="card">
                <span class="badge">即将推出</span>
                <h2>💻 Microsoft (MSFT) 深度分析</h2>
                <p>科技巨头能否突破历史新高？</p>
            </a>
            
            <a href="/stock-analysis/googl-20260331/" class="card">
                <span class="badge">即将推出</span>
                <h2>🔍 Google (GOOGL) 深度分析</h2>
                <p>短期回调还是长期买入机会？</p>
            </a>
            
            <a href="/stock-analysis/meta-20260331/" class="card">
                <span class="badge">即将推出</span>
                <h2>👍 Meta (META) 深度分析</h2>
                <p>股价突破后的投资机会与风险分析</p>
            </a>
            
            <a href="/stock-analysis/amzn-20260331/" class="card">
                <span class="badge">即将推出</span>
                <h2>📦 Amazon (AMZN) 深度分析</h2>
                <p>突破 200 美元关口后能否延续涨势？</p>
            </a>
            
            <a href="/stock-analysis/amd-20260331/" class="card">
                <span class="badge">即将推出</span>
                <h2>⚡ AMD 深度分析</h2>
                <p>短期回调还是长期买入机会？</p>
            </a>
        </div>
        
        <footer>
            <p>&copy; 2026 AI Market Insight. All rights reserved.</p>
        </footer>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
